We have 
 $\begin{align*} \boxed{\boxed{11}}&=\boxed{1+11} \\ &=\boxed{12} \\ &=1+2+3+4+6+12 \\ &=28, \end{align*}$ 
from which the answer is $$\boxed{\textbf{(D)}\ 28}.$$ ~Aplus95 (Fundamental Logic) ~MRENTHUSIASM (Reconstruction)

